taskprerequisites.screen:
[libdefaults] default_realm = EXAMPLE.COM
[realms] EXAMPLE.COM = { kdc = dc.example.com admin_server = dc.example.com kpasswd_server = dc.example.com kpasswd_protocol = SET_CHANGE }
[domain_realm] .example.com = EXAMPLE.COM

task.procedure:
&rolestepsmb;
Remove a CIFS share.# sharemgr remove-share -s share-path group-name
For example, to remove share /sales/share1 from share group mysharegroup, type:# sharemgr remove-share -s /sales/share1 mysharegroup
